1
00:00:01,430 --> 00:00:03,271
Is that you, John?
是你吗,John?

2
00:00:03,919 --> 00:00:05,791
Yes, speaking.
是我.

3
00:00:06,711 --> 00:00:11,108
Tell Mary we'll be late for dinner this evening.
你告诉Mary,今晚吃饭我们将晚到一会儿.

4
00:00:11,570 --> 00:00:14,787
I'm afraid I don't understand.
我恐怕我还不明白你的意思.

5
00:00:15,058 --> 00:00:17,591
Hasn't Mary told you?
Mary没有告诉你吗?

6
00:00:18,136 --> 00:00:22,539
She invited Charlotte and me to dinner this evening.
她邀请我和Charlotte今晚去吃饭.

7
00:00:22,950 --> 00:00:28,123
I said I would be at your house at six o'clock,
我说过我6点到你家,

8
00:00:28,768 --> 00:00:33,215
but the boss wants me to do some extra work.
但是老板想让我做点额外的工作.

9
00:00:33,499 --> 00:00:36,384
I'll have to stay at the office.
我不得不留在办公室,

10
00:00:36,655 --> 00:00:39,358
I don't know when I'll finish.
我不知道什么时候才能结束.

11
00:00:40,078 --> 00:00:47,478
Oh, and by the way, my wife wants to know if Mary needs any help.
Oh,顺便问一问,我妻子想知道Mary是否需要帮忙.

12
00:00:48,297 --> 00:00:52,029
I don't know what you're talking about.
我不知道你在说些什么.

13
00:00:52,326 --> 00:00:55,688
That is John Smith, isn't it?
你是John Smith,对吗?

14
00:00:56,006 --> 00:00:58,441
Yes, I'm John Smith.
是的,我是John Smith.

15
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:04,153
You are John Smith,the engineer,aren't you? 
你是工程师John Smith,对吗?

16
00:01:04,544 --> 00:01:05,752
That's right.
对.

17
00:01:06,933 --> 00:01:12,619
You work for the Overseas Engineering Company, don't you? 
你在海外工程公司上班,是吗?

18
00:01:13,024 --> 00:01:19,244
No, I don't. I'm John Smith the telephone engineer
不,不是.我是电话工程师John Smith,

19
00:01:19,723 --> 00:01:23,421
and I'm repairing your telephone line.
我正在修理你的电话线.

